data.description: Sophisticated Victorian style home with a modern touch located in Los Fresnos, TX. This gorgeous custom designed home is overflowing with upgrades and exudes elegance from every angle. Open concept floor plan, two living areas, and an extra-large mudroom. Satisfy even the most demanding chef with the gourmet kitchen, boasting custom cabinetry & granite counter tops. State-of-the art light fixtures & tile flooring throughout. 3 generously sized bedrooms all located on the second level, there is plenty of space for the entire family. Primary bedroom features an extra-large closet & luxurious spa bathroom with double vanities, an extra large spa-like shower, and an elegant clawfoot tub. Entertain guests year-round in the fully fenced & private back yard with side gated driveway. Conveniently located less then 22 miles from South Padre Island & only 30 miles to the SpaceX Launch Facility!!!
